---
title: Mexican-Spiced Grilled Tilapia Tacos with Pineapple-Jalapeño Salsa and Lime Crema
description: Grilled tilapia? Let's taco 'bout it! We've brought in some Mexican flavour favourites to create punchy tilapia tacos for a night in the backyard. You're looking at a base of creamy coleslaw, topped with smoky tilapia, fresh lime crema and a sweet-meets-heat pineapple-jalapeño salsa!
